1 name your website
2 register for doap.com create a hostname-nicapiscina.doap.com
3 create user id and home directory and public_html folder in doap.com
4 usradd -m nicapiscina
5 mkdir /home/nicapiscina/public_html
6 tar -xzvf /root/new_site.tar.gz /home/nicapiscina/public_html
7 mysqladmin -u root -pfr1ck0ff create nicapiscina
cp /home/nicapiscina/public_html/wp-config.php.sample /home/nicapiscina/public_html/wp-config.php
edit wp-config.php and change db name to nicapiscina
put the name nicapiscina.doap.com into named dns servers
restart webserver and dns server

